          "reviewBody": "Visites this school last week for the BOSCOTSAV 2023 representing Carmel school as the sports teacher and I was so loved by the entire campus and the faculty and obviously the students . They're indeed so well disciplined and very much helping out. Kudos to the entire DON BOSCO famoly",
