          },
          "reviewBody": "A CBSC affiliated school at Liluah. Huge campus. Road infront of school is narrow and very busy. Every year they organise a huge interschool competition named \"Boscotsav\". There are two maingate gate1 and gate2. These gates are situated in two different road. So please check the gate number before entering to the school.",
          "publisher": {
